						<div class="postbody">Another question: Is there a place where I can see some statistical data of the music of various games? I'm especially interested in the size of the soundtracks. For example: How many bytes in the ROM does the standard melody of &quot;Super Mario Bros.&quot; occupy and what methods were used to compress it?</div>

					
